    "Title": "Bounty Apprehension Reevaluation",
    "Description": "ABOUT THE JOB\nWhile your past performance has not been to our standards, microTech Protection Services has decided to offer you a chance to redeem yourself. \n\nTo reevaluate your skills, we would like you to apprehend ~mission(TargetName) from ~mission(Location|Address).\n\nRESPONSIBILITIES\n\u2022 Provide own transportation to ~mission(Location|Address).\n\u2022 Neutralize ~mission(TargetName); using force as necessary.\n\nMINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Bounty Hunters Guild membership and appropriate certification.\n\u2022 Access to vehicle suitably outfitted for combat.\n\u2022 Available for immediate deployment.\n\nPREFERRED QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Ability to handle high pressure situations.",
